Adebayo Obajemu Transcorp Hotel on Wednesday notified the Nigerian Stock Exchange and the investing public of the closed period of the company to finalize a proposed Rights Issue. In a statement signed by the company secretary Chike Anikwe, the group stated thus: “The Board of Directors of Transcorp Hotels Plc has scheduled its 73rd Board meeting to hold on June 3rd, 2020, to consider a Rights Issue of the Company.” Consequently, the Company hereby notifies the Exchange of the commencement of its closed period from May 19, 2020 up to twenty-four (24) hours after the publication of the Rights Issue. All Transcorp Hotels Plc insiders have been duly informed accordingly